rows.label: tlk45300021_02_msg0001
rows.name:
My brother is a member of the
Superbian Military Engineer Corps.

rows.label: tlk45300021_02_msg0002
rows.name:
It's a dangerous job that mostly
involves transporting Core Crystals.

rows.label: tlk45300021_02_msg0003
rows.name:
It's only thanks to my brother's
influence that I was even able to move
all the way out here to Trigo.

rows.label: tlk45300021_02_msg0004
rows.name:
But now this Iira lot have shown up
in Trigo... Apparently they even got
away from Special Inquisitor Meleph.

rows.label: tlk45300021_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe we would've been better off
living a quiet life back in Superbia
after all...
